pl.edu.icm.cermine.structure.model

Class BxPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.edu.icm.cermine.structure.model.BxObject<BxZone,BxPage,BxDocument>
      • pl.edu.icm.cermine.structure.model.BxPage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<BxZone>, Indexable<BxPage>, Printable

    public final class BxPage
extends BxObject<BxZone,BxPage,BxDocument>
    Models a single page of a document. A page is either segmented (divided into zones) or not segmented (containing a list of chunks that haven't been grouped into zones yet).
    Author:
    Dominika Tkaczyk (d.tkaczyk@icm.edu.pl)
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
